<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>URL Shortener Microservice</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css"></style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row p-2 p-sm-5">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h1 class="header">
                    URL Shortener Microservice
                </h1>
                <hr />
            </div>
            <div class="col-12">
                <h3>
                    How it works
                </h3>
                <blockquote>I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.
                    When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link.
                </blockquote>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12">
                <h3>
                    Example usage
                </h3>
                <blockquote>
                    <code>http://myurlshorti.herokuapp.com/api/your_url_here.com</your></code><br />
                    <code>http://myurlshorti.herokuapp.com/api/google.com</code><br />
                    <code>http://myurlshorti.herokuapp.com/api/youtube.com</code>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12">
                <h3>
                    Example output
                </h3>
                <blockquote>
                    <code>
                        {"url":"myurlshorti.herokuapp.com/api/url/96203"}
                    </code>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12">
                <h3>
                    Usage
                </h3>
                <blockquote>
                    <code>
                        myurlshorti.herokuapp.com/api/url/96203
                    </code>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12">
                <h3>
                    Will redirect to
                </h3>
                <blockquote>
                    <code>
                        https://www.google.com/
                    </code>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>